short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Changes the appearance of Google Colab!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will enhance your data science experience by allowing you to change the style of Google Colab much more than a simple dark mode or light mode! By importing your own themes from VS Code, or using any of the 56 provided themes, your Google Colab experience will be transformed by your favorite theme changing the way you see your code and data.
